## 6. Migration Path for `mediaService.ts`

The current `mediaService.ts` does four distinct jobs in one class. The refactor splits them:

| Current Responsibility | V2 Module | File |
|---|---|---|
| FFmpeg.wasm lifecycle | `FFmpegFallback` | `src/lib/media/ffmpegFallback.ts` |
| Frame capture loop | `FrameCapturer` | `src/lib/media/frameCapturer.ts` |
| Format-specific encoding | `WebCodecsEncoder` / `FFmpegEncoder` | `src/lib/media/encoder.ts` |
| Progress reporting | `ExportService` (orchestrator) | `src/lib/services/exportService.ts` |

The `appState.renderComposition()` method (lines 955-1044) gets replaced by:
```typescript
// In appState.svelte.ts (slim):
async renderComposition(format, options) {
  const { exportService } = await import('$lib/services/exportService');
  const blob = await exportService.export(this.renderedSvg, format, options);
  await this.saveBlobToDisk(blob, `sumosized-render.${format}`);
}
```

