## 8. Performance Targets

| Metric | Current | V2 Target |
|---|---|---|
| FFmpeg load time | 20s timeout (broken) | 0ms (Mediabunny, no WASM load) |
| GIF export (3s @ 24fps, 1080²) | Untestable (timeout) | < 30s (FFmpeg.wasm ST, CDN cached) |
| MP4 export (3s @ 24fps, 1080²) | Untestable (timeout) | < 10s (WebCodecs HW accelerated) |
| Main thread blocking during export | 100% (synchronous loop) | 0% (Worker + OffscreenCanvas) |
| Repo clone size | ~100MB | ~70MB (after removing vendored WASM) |
| Initial page load (no export) | Fast | Same (Mediabunny is lazy-loaded) |

